data.description: Discover this stunning one-bedroom condo with an open floor plan that immerses you in captivating nature views from both the living room and bedroom. Enjoy an upgraded kitchen, a spacious walk-in closet, and the convenience of single-level living. This unit also features underground heated parking and incredible shared amenities including an indoor pool, hot tub, modern fitness center, and clubhouse. Located near shopping, dining, parks, and trails, this condo offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility, with two major highways nearby for easy commuting. Your next home awaits!
